first_para: John Zak Woodcock (born 14 October 1978) is a British Labour Co-operative politician who has been the Member of Parliament (MP) for Barrow and Furness since 2010.

full.extract:
John Zak Woodcock (born 14 October 1978) is a British Labour Co-operative politician who has been the Member of Parliament (MP) for Barrow and Furness since 2010.
